title: 133. American Privilege
itunes:title: 133. American Privilege
description:
Are you starting to see your American privilege now? On today's episode, Andy and the crew talk about what transpired in Afghanistan earlier this week, the mask & vaccine mandates and how we can unite as Americans to save America.
